<html i18n:domain="opencore" metal:use-macro="here/@@standard_macros/master">
  <head>
    <title metal:fill-slot="title" tal:content="string:Invite - ${view/area/Title}" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="content">
    
    <div class="oc-headingBlock">
      <h1>Invite users</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div id="oc-content-main">
        <p class="oc-headingContext">Send an email to invite people to join</p>
        <form id="oc-inviteByEmail" name="oc-inviteByEmail"
              tal:attributes="action view/request/ACTUAL_URL"
              method="POST">
        <div class="oc-headingBlock">
          <label for="email-invites">To:</label>
        </div>

          <textarea style="width: 90%;" rows="3" cols="20" id="email-invites" name="email-invites"
                    tal:content="view/request/form/email-invites | nothing" />
          <p class="oc-discreetText">Comma separated, or one-per-line</p>


					<label for="subject">Subject:</label>
          <input type="text" name="subject" i18n:attributes="value email_invite_email_subject" value="Invitation to join a project"><br>

					From: <span tal:content="python: view.portal.getProperty('email_from_address')" /><br/>

					<label for="message">Message:</label>
          <textarea rows="20" cols="70"  name="message" i18n:translate="email_invite_default_body">
<span i18n:name="inviter_name" tal:replace="python: view.loggedinmember.getFullname() or view.loggedinmember.id" /> has invited you to join "<span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" />" on <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />.
 
<span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" /> is a free toolset for social change. With <span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" />, you can build collaborative pages for organizing projects. You can also blog, set up mailing lists, store and share files, and keep track of tasks.
 
We hope you'll take <span i18n:name="portal_url" tal:replace="view/portal/absolute_url" /> for a spin.

Cheers,
The <span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" /> Team
</textarea><br>

This will be added to all messages:
<div style="background-color: light blue;">
<pre i18n:translate="email_invite_static_body">
<span i18n:name="user_message"></span>
To accept this invitation or learn more about the project, click here: 
<span i18n:name="project_title">[url]</span>.
This message was sent from <span i18n:name="portal_title"
tal:replace="view/portal_title" />.  

To contact <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />, go here:
<span
i18n:name="site_contact_url" tal:replace="string: ${view/portal/absolute_url}/contact-site-admin" />
</pre> </div>


          <input type="submit" name="task|email-invites" value="Send"
                 class="oc-button" />
        </form>

      </div>
          
    </div><!-- end content-fill-slot -->
  </body>
</html>
